{"tid":1213162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我一早已經講左去十幾次有任何行動唔好信呢度","createTime":"2019-06-13T00:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T02:46:52.000Z","uid":8687,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4597e7289c11018acde56a27e4e1654ef5a4beef","tid":1213162,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"去過既人都知理場根本好難上網<br />\n義士亦唔會有時間上網何況開 post?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去到現場覺得對方岩傾自己用app加對方</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先<br />\n我唔認同衝<br />\n衝完留唔到人永恆結局<br />\n你永遠唔會夠狗抽亦係事實<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但你地堅持要做的話<br />\n唔好係度開 post 有乜行動亦唔好信呢度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你當呢度開post 話要點做既都係仇思達既分身你就明我講乜野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"bea5b39e26bc28829b8020beb8a8d10099f6d91c","tid":1213162,"uid":223374,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5ee88ab22305cc5ad5b1d8a96d4fc9e5878cf06","tid":1213162,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7247d7afc1a6315a18404db479e22c15269b5a87","tid":1213162,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8828b82291ede841db61655bd7b4bc6bbf57f1ad","tid":1213162,"uid":8687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"二樓已經想搞鳩我呢個 post 証明我講冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee84c380c34266f97a6082a67e9c857495f6dcfd","tid":1213162,"uid":51724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:53:16.000Z"