>\n<br />\n勇武拆啲磚出黎，其實係嚇走好多和理非<br />\n同埋爭取沉默大多數係要靠和理非<br />\n勇武俾人打，啲50、60、70後會覺得抵死"},{"pid":"fa97ce36208d5d0bd57ca4eef4f3ac870862bd15","tid":1213162,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f14b352f7f209aac6dc52b1a5eb7048bafe104b","tid":1213162,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}